title: Parkland, Liberty reach EPC championship
text:
Parkland, Liberty reach EPC championship Published: 11:43 PM EDT Oct 22, 2015 
Parkland and Liberty both posted impressive EPC girls volleyball semifinal wins Thursday night. 
Both teams swept their semifinals, advancing to Saturday's EPC girls volleyball championship. 
Top-seeded Parkland beat No. 4 Central Catholic 3-0, while No. 2 Liberty posted a 3-0 win over No. 3 Nazareth. 
Saturday's title match between Liberty and Parkland will be played at 1pm at Whitehall High School.
